Name: Cracked
About the game: Wishlist and follow, if you're interested in Cracked Cracked is a difficult 2D Platformer. Dominate the leaderboards by completing the maps as fast as possible. Explore the abandoned Factory, the desert Pyramid and the jungle Temple. EXPLORE VARIOUS LOCATIONS From all the locations, you can choose which one to explore first. CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER It's up to you how you want to customize your character. DOMINATE THE LEADERBOARDS Finish the maps as fast as you can and put your name on the leaderboard. You can either compete against your own personal best, your friends or the world. DEFEAT THE BOSS Save your friends by defeating the boss in every campaign's last map, and unlock them as a playable character. It's your choice who you think is worthy of being saved first. /
